   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="DLA_85.1.3171_00069"/>Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb428">Welsberg im Pusterthal</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb723">Wildbad-Hôtel</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="DLA_85.1.3171_00068"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb40808">Palast Hôtel Lido</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb465">Riva <hi rend="superscript">a</hi>/Gardasee</rs></hi>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="left"><pb facs="DLA_85.1.3171_00068"/><date when="1901-08-15">15. Augu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</date>.</dateline></opener><p>Es i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t kühl und <unclear>kö</unclear><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tlich hier. Aber ein<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>am. Bitte, lieber <hi rend="latintype">Arthur</hi>, hol’ auch meine <hi rend="latintype">Poste
                  restante</hi> Briefe von der Po<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t u. heb’<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ie mir auf, damit ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ie <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03079-1"/><date when="1901-08-18">Sonntag</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03079-1">Am <date when="1901-08-18">Sonntag</date>, dem <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1901-08-18" subtype="date-only"/> kam <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Goldmann</rs> in
                     <rs type="place" ref="#pmb428">Welsberg</rs> an. <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> war bereits seit <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1901-08-15" subtype="date-only"/> dort. Am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1901-08-26" subtype="date-only"/> reiste <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> weiter nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb40454">Villach</rs>, <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11485">Goldmann</rs>
                  nach <rs type="place" ref="#pmb44278">Pörtschach</rs>.</note> finde. Herzliche
               Grüße an alle! <signed>P. G.</signed></p></div>
      </body>
